{"tid":708767,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥倫比亞球員擺烏龍被槍殺","createTime":"2018-06-19T13:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T01:27:35.000Z","uid":78873,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"faa0edf1c362c712264ffb7dc9b445eba7ef254a","tid":708767,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"1994年6月，於美國舉行第15屆世界盃足球賽，被編於A組的哥倫比亞首場敗予羅馬尼亞，不少哥倫比亞的球迷都將希望放在哥倫比亞對美國的賽事身上。然而，擔任後衛的哥倫比亞隊長艾斯高巴，於攔截美國隊的傳中球時，誤將皮球踢入己隊龍門，令哥倫比亞以1比2敗予美國，以小組最後一名成績出局。<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞球員於被淘汰後返國，至7月2日凌晨，艾斯高巴與朋友到酒吧消遣後，獨自到停車場取車，三名男子突然出現與他爭執，其中兩名男子更取出點三八口徑手槍，近距離槍撃艾斯高巴達六槍之多（有說十多槍），艾斯高巴送院後45分鐘後死亡。<br />\n<br />\nC山齊士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e22cf9032ea97c7f86beb91790305adaf4a520c","tid":708767,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"Escobar <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d609e5c09c57e87c9ac2a7e4ed7fb27f6853cfb","tid":708767,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"千其唔好番哥倫比亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c572596b804abb7a8eedd0436c40220797889dd0","tid":708767,"uid":156508,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:01:27.000Z","msg":"條友係都俾阿士東維拉郁佢先 <br />\n早兩年都係佢廢間接搞到維拉降班"},{"pid":"5bd9388b1821cc690f16f9391acd11e182f375be","tid":708767,"uid":78873,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://playerswiki.com/uploads/thumb/carlos-sanchez-moreno-300-300.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplayerswiki.com%2Fuploads%2Fthumb%2Fcarlos-sanchez-moreno-300-300.jpeg&h=5d6f38a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br